{"data":[{"date":"19:09 09/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 09/08: \u201cHarry Maguire ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn MU\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-0908-hlv-leicester-harry-magui-chac-chan-den-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 09/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Leicester: \u201cHarry Maguire ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn MU\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 0908 Maguire \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 0908 Maguire \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-0908-Maguire-den-MU-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Claude Puel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Maguire s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn MU v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, HLV Claude Puel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn MU: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Manchester, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Old Trafford 2 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa M.U v\u00e0 Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. Maguire s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi\u00a0Leicester h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd\u201d.</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e0 phi l\u00fd: \u201c T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 8 ch\u1ee9c V\u0110QG v\u00e0 3 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n suy ngh\u0129 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.\u201d<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718-172-194127.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718-172-194127.html\">Mourinho: \u201cM.U \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 NHA ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec\u2026 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng\u201d</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.  \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e0 phi l\u00fd.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Yerry Mina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca b\u00e1n Yerry Mina cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Atletico</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Diego Godin trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Jerome Boateng, Toby Alderweireld, Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Harry Maguire.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Leicester</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \"bom x\u1ecbt\" c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 0908 Harry Maguire ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 0908 Harry Maguire ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-0908-Harry-Maguire-chac-chan-den-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>West Ham mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Perez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal-172-194121.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-0908-Harry-Maguire-chac-chan-den-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal-172-194121.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span><br>\r\nWest Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho bi quan v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e0i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, HLV Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a MU, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u00edt \u1ecfi \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Ligue 1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1eeba sang Chelsea, bom t\u1ea5n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u01a1 l\u00e0m huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Chelea, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u00fap CLB gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real n\u00edu k\u00e9o Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Inter</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/real-madrid-muon-giu-chan-luka-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Luka Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Luka Modric. Inter Milan \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh b\u1eb1ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft \u1edf Real, Marcelo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5306","checkdouble":"194130"},{"date":"05:59 10/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 10/8: Mourinho \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Godin l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-108-mourinho-dien-tiet-vi-bi-phia-godin-loi-dung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/8.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Godin l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 108 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 108 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/mu-nhan-don-dau-tren-ttcn.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Godin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u201cch\u1ebft \u0111u\u1ed1i v\u1edb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ecdc\u201d khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alderweireld, Maguire, Mina hay Boateng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, sau c\u00f9ng th\u00ec MU c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Godin m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9, k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Jose Mourinho t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh l\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ra l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi k\u00fd k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 7,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro/n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi MU trong ng\u00e0y deadline<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 108 Mourinho \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Godin l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 108 Mourinho \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Godin l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/7/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-108-Mourinho-dien-tiet-vi-bi-phia-Godin-loi-dung-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Timothy Fosu-Mensah</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tu nghi\u1ec7p \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace, Timothy Fosu-Mensah tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 MU nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Th\u1ebf l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ed1i ren v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb 20 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i chia tay CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n v\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Fosu-Mensah l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u r\u1eddi Man Utd trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, sau hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Sam Johnstone v\u00e0 Joel Pereira c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ba h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind, Cameron Borthwick-Jackson v\u00e0 Axel Tuanzebe. K\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp trong ba tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh trong ng\u00e0y deadline<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Daniel Arzani: Melbourne City \u2013 Manchester City, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u1edf Celtic<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Mateo Kovacic: Real Madrid \u2013 Chelsea, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Lucas Perez: Arsenal \u2013 West Ham, 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Leander Dendoncker: Anderlecht \u2013 Wolverhampton, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic toi Chelsea\" title=\"Kovacic toi Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Kovacic-toi-Chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mateo Kovacic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Bernard: Shakhtar Donetsk \u2013 Everton, mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Carlos Sanchez: Fiorentina \u2013 West Ham, kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Jordan Ayew: Swansea \u2013 Crystal Palace, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Caglar Soyuncu: Freiburg \u2013 Leiceter, 19 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Harry Arter: Bournemouth \u2013 Cardiff, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"West Ham mua thanh cong Lucas Perez\" title=\"West Ham mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Perez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-0908-Harry-Maguire-chac-chan-den-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lucas Perez</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Federico Fernandez: Swansea \u2013 Newcastle, 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Luciano Vietto: Atletico Madrid \u2013 Fulham, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yerry Mina: Barcelona \u2013 Everton, 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Andre Gomes: Barcelona \u2013 Everton, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina va Andre Gomes\" title=\"Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Andre Gomes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/gettyimages-1014015780.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Andre Gomes</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Timothy Fosu-Mensah: Manchester United \u2013 Fulham, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Andre-Frank Zambo Anguissa: Marseille \u2013 Fulham, 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Danny Ings: Liverpool \u2013 Southampton, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5305","checkdouble":"194143"},{"date":"18:50 09/08","title":"Barca \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Yerry Mina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/barca-dong-y-de-yerry-mina-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-voi-gia-34-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca b\u00e1n Yerry Mina cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua h\u1ee5t Mina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca b\u00e1n Yerry Mina cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca b\u00e1n Yerry Mina cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Barca-ban-Yerry-Mina-cho-Everton-voi-gia-34-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Yerry Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Yerry Mina, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. T\u1edd Mirror c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Man \u0111\u1ecf d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 \u1edf ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i khi M.U t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 Mina v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mina s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-yerry-mina-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-nhung-khong-phai-mu-172-193827.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca b\u00e1n Yerry Mina cho Everton</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton dat duoc thoa thuan mua Mina voi gia 40 trieu bang\" title=\"Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Mina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Mina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u&nbsp;b\u1ea3ng. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong \u00edt gi\u1edd t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia, Everton c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3n Andre Gomes c\u0169ng t\u1eeb Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Goodison Park theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Mina v\u00e0 Andre Gomes, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Everton s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Digne t\u1eeb Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 b\u1ecf ra 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Richarlison.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 5 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5304","checkdouble":"194126"},{"date":"19:38 09/08","title":"Thibaut Courtois CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Los Blancos l\u00e0 CLB t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u00e1ng nay, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/CHINH-THUC-Thibaut-Courtois-ra-mat-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois \u0111\u1ebfn Real v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean Real c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. Courtois sau \u0111\u00f3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real, anh mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Madrid g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. The Blues r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1eeb Courtois v\u00e0 Real khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge kh\u00f4ng thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Los Blancos l\u00e0 CLB t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois ra mat Real Madrid\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid, khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Chelsea nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho Real, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap Real thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCourtois nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Navas \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Real \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, \u1edf World Cup 2018 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5303","checkdouble":"194131"},{"date":"20:53 09/08","title":"Coutinho CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C k\u1ebf th\u1eeba s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Figo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/coutinho-chinh-thuc-ke-thua-so-ao-cua-huyen-thoai-figo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Philippe Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb s\u1ed1 \u00e1o 14 \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y s\u00e1ng s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Coutinho m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14 khi m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, Barca \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Philippe Coutinho t\u1eeb Liverpool. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u1edf H\u00e8 2017 song The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Philippe Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Philippe Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Philippe-Coutinho-khoac-ao-so-7-o-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Coutinho \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14 khi m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0110\u00f4ng 2018, sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 160 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCoutinho l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 to\u00e0n n\u0103ng khi ghi b\u00e0n hay ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou, Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 m\u00e0 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Coutinho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Philippe Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb s\u1ed1 \u00e1o 14 \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y s\u00e1ng s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho khoac ao so 7 o Barca tu mua giai toi\" title=\"Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/coutinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00c1o s\u1ed1 7 do ti\u00ea\u0300n v\u00ea\u0323 Arda Turan \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y khi m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, Barca \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Antoine Griezmann c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid, h\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, Coutinho \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. Chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou, bao g\u1ed3m Luis Figo (1995-2000), Eidur Gudjohnsen (2006-2010) hay David Villa (2010-2013).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCoutinho v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Brazil, anh v\u00e0 Selecao \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Barca \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5302","checkdouble":"194134"},{"date":"22:31 09/08","title":"Atletico Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/atletico-madrid-chinh-thuc-co-tien-dao-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a AC Milan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico quan t\u00e2m Nikola Kalinic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, AC Milan g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Nikola Kalinic b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/CHINH-THUC-Atletico-Madrid-mua-Nikola-Kalinic-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nicola Kalinic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Atletico quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a AC Milan v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 30 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A, song anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi Higuain c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n San Siro. Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/atletico-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-tien-dao-moi-180-193893.html\" target=\"_blank\">Atletico Madrid quan t\u00e2m Nikola Kalinic</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Kevin Gameiro ra \u0111i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nValencia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kevin Gameiro, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n Atletico mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nikola Kalinic h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Kalinic, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kalinic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a AC Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nikola Kalinic chinh thuc gia nhap Atletico Madrid\" title=\"Nikola Kalinic ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/atletico-madrid-chinh-thuc-co-tien-dao-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nikola Kalinic ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: \u201cAtletico de Madrid v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 30 tu\u1ed5i Nikola Kalinic. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKalinic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Kalinic l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho Atletico, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i ghi 33 b\u00e0n sau 84 tr\u1eadn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Fiorentina, anh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Mian v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2017. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 ch\u1ec9 ghi 6 b\u00e0n sau 31 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG anh c\u00f3 15 b\u00e0n sau 42 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng Kalinic \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb HLV Dalic \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn anh m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1eaft NHM Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5301","checkdouble":"194137"},{"date":"22:17 09/08","title":"Thibaut Courtois khi\u1ebfn Chelsea cay c\u00fa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/19/thibaut-courtois-khien-chelsea-cay-cu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois mu\u1ed1n Hazard t\u1edbi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i gi\u1edd, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid, anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois Hazard\" title=\"Courtois Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/12/thich-the-hien-hazard-bi-dong-doi-chelsea-mang-te-tat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois mu\u1ed1n Hazard t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Hazard h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi t\u00f4i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 Hazard l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac n\u1ebfu anh \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u00ecnh \u1edf Real&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Hazard, anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Bernabeu. T\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real, t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Courtois khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt NHM c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Courtois c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid</span>, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Bernabeu v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real, Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real, Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Cap-ben-Real,-Thibaut-Courtois-phat-bieu-ve-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thibaut Courtois gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao ch\u1ecdn Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Real v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n, t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Real b\u1edfi t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i gia \u0111\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;H\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid, hy v\u1ecdng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5300","checkdouble":"194138"},{"date":"22:54 09/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, HLV Lee Johnson c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a The Blues.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jay Dasilva kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Jay Dasilva c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Chelsea n\u0103m 13 tu\u1ed5i, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Jay-Dasilva-roi-Chelsea-cap-ben-Bristol-City-theo-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jay Dasilva kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea9y Jay Dasilva t\u1edbi Charlton Athletic theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 m\u00f9a, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Charlton c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 48 l\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jay Dasilva ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Bristol City</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, HLV Lee Johnson c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a The Blues.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jay Dasilva chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Jay Dasilva ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City, Jay Dasilva s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJay Dasilva t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c U16, U17, U18, U19 v\u00e0 U20 Anh, NHM Chelsea \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5299","checkdouble":"194139"},{"date":"23:16 09/08","title":"Yerry Mina CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/yerry-mina-chinh-thuc-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Yerry Mina r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park. Barca \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 30,2 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf World Cup 2018, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Yerry Mina r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Yerry Mina r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/yerry-mina-chinh-thuc-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mina ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-mina-172-193764.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Mina</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 v\u00ec Man \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEverton sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i. S\u1ef1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Everton c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Yerry Mina r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park. Barca \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 30,2 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 1.5 tri\u1ec7u euro ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Mina. Barca c\u0169ng k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mina l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Everton</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 11,8 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Mina t\u1eeb Palmeiras, ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng h\u1ecd b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30,2 tri\u1ec7u euro. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton dat duoc thoa thuan mua Mina voi gia 40 trieu bang\" title=\"Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Mina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mina l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, Mina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994, Everton \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 25 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Digne t\u1eeb Barca v\u00e0 chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Richarlison t\u1eeb Watford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, HLV Marco Silva \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 6 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5298","checkdouble":"194140"},{"date":"23:41 09/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: \"Bom x\u1ecbt\" Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-bom-xit-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Andre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 m\u00f9a, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 2.25 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andre Gomes mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Barca. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 10 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Andre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Andre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/CHINH-THUC-Andre-Gomes-roi-Barca-toi-Everton-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andre Gomes mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi khi Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho ra \u0111i, song s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Arthur v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, Andre Gomes \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Camp Nou. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u sao Valencia ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Andre Gomes, M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Andre Gomes \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, song kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Andre Gomes ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Everton</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 m\u00f9a, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 2.25 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andre Gomes toi Everton theo dang cho muon mot mua\" title=\"Andre Gomes t\u1edbi Everton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-bom-xit-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andre Gomes t\u1edbi Everton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEverton \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Andre Gomes c\u1ee7a Barca. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park chi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Barca, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Andre Gomes m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Barca song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Everton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAndre Gomes l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/yerry-mina-chinh-thuc-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-194140.html\" target=\"_blank\">Everton mua Mina </span>v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30,2 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 Digne v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5297","checkdouble":"194141"},{"date":"04:56 10/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Southampton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-southampton-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tien-dao-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Ings mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Ings kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho Liverpool. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Ings ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/Danny-Ings-toi-Southampton-theo-dang-cho-muon-mot-mua-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Ings mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Sturridge, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Origi theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Trong tay HLV Klopp \u0111ang c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong. Ngo\u00e0i Ings \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Firmino, Sturridge, Origi v\u00e0 Solanke.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Liverpool c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, Danny Ings \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSouthampton mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Southampton m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Danny Ings</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Ings toi Southampton theo dang cho muon\" title=\"Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-southampton-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tien-dao-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSouthampton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Ings trong th\u1eddi gian m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf s\u00e2n St Mary.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Mark Hughes d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Ings, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Crystal Palace, Watford v\u00e0 Wolves \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Liverpool song ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Southampton \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)<br>\r\nDanny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton, Danny Ings c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Southampton</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5296","checkdouble":"194142"},{"date":"15:21 09/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh Barca s\u1eafp chia tay v\u1ee3","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/tan-binh-barca-sap-chia-tay-vo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arturo Vidal th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eabn hay t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o r\u1eb1ng ph\u00eda sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a anh c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a t\u1edbi hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef l\u00e0 m\u1eb9 v\u00e0 v\u1ee3. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd th\u00ec b\u00e2n binh Barcelona n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb. V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u01a1m ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0nh, canh ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ecdt.</h2><h2>V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Vidal chia t\u00e1ch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Marca ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Vidal \u0111ang b\u00ean mi\u1ec7ng v\u1ef1c. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 31 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile v\u00e0 c\u00f4 v\u1ee3 Maria Teresa Matus \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n chung s\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi nhau n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTin \u0111\u1ed3n \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf. Th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec m\u1ed7i khi c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00e3nh di\u1ec7n d\u1eabn theo ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ee3 con. V\u1eady m\u00e0 khi Vidal tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng Barcelona, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng Maria Teresa \u0111\u00e2u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n c\u1ecf Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Vidal chia tay v\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n c\u1ecf Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Vidal chia tay v\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/vidal2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Vidal th\u1eddi c\u00f2n m\u1eb7n n\u1ed3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Instagram c\u1ee7a Vidal c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n khoe \u1ea3nh c\u00e1c con. Ch\u1ee9 Vidal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n khoe \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Maria Teresa nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 v\u00ec sao v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Vidal l\u1ea1i c\u01a1m ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0nh, canh ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ecdt nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Maria Teresa v\u00e0 Vidal g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ly th\u00e2n. D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c fan kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVidal v\u00e0 Maria Teresa \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi nhau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f2n 10 n\u0103m. Ch\u00e0ng quen n\u00e0ng t\u1eeb h\u1ed3i 2008. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f3 Vidal c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Leverkusen. Maria Teresa th\u00ec b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea7m l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu, cho d\u00f9 c\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u00ednh d\u00e1ng t\u1edbi l\u00e0ng th\u1eddi trang. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p b\u1eb1ng tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Vidal n\u00e0y s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau m\u1eabu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m 2009, Vidal c\u01b0\u1edbi Maria Teresa. C\u00f4 theo anh phi\u00eau l\u01b0u chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, t\u1eeb Leverkusen sang Juventus r\u1ed3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Bayern. Maria Teresa \u0111\u00e3 sinh h\u1ea1 cho Vidal ba\u00a0 thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n nh\u1ecf g\u1ed3m Alonso, Elisabetta v\u00e0 Emiliano. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd Vidal \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Bayern sang Barca, nh\u01b0ng Maria Teresa th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n theo anh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng fan hi\u1ebfu k\u1ef3 th\u00eam t\u00f2 m\u00f2. H\u1ecd t\u00f2 m\u00f2 ch\u1edd xem Vidal s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea5m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u00f2 m\u00f2 ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng xem chuy\u1ec7n c\u01a1m ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0nh, canh ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ecdt c\u1ee7a v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Vidal th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e1 b\u00f3ng gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1o hi\u1ebfu m\u1eb9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef ph\u00eda sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vidal gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Maria Teresa. Song anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 coi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap anh n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u00e2n m\u1eabu Jacqueline Pardo c\u1ee7a anh. Vidal t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 r\u1eb1ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n quan tr\u1ecdng khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 v\u00ec m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVidal ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201cK\u00fd \u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n t\u00f4i nh\u1edb v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n \u0111\u00f3i v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n l\u1ea1nh m\u00e0 t\u00f4i v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea7n t\u1ea3o khuya s\u1edbm th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n trang tr\u1ea3i cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00f4i nh\u1edb nh\u01b0 in h\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi 14 tu\u1ed5i. M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i \u0111i l\u00e0m v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed9n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e0 l\u1ea3 \u0111i. B\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 nh\u1ee7 l\u00f2ng m\u00ecnh r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf m\u00e3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n gi\u00fap m\u1eb9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh lam l\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u1eb9, t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i t\u1ef1 nh\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c g\u1ea5p ba, g\u1ea5p b\u1ed1n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed g\u1ea5p m\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau n\u00e0y khi t\u00f4i th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p r\u1ed3i, nh\u1eefng k\u00fd \u1ee9c \u1ea5y v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng th\u00f4i th\u00fac t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua tu\u1ed5i th\u01a1 c\u01a1 c\u1ef1c, Vidal t\u1ef1 giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 cho m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c con ph\u1ea3i kh\u1ed5 nh\u01b0 anh ng\u00e0y x\u01b0a. Gi\u1edd anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho 3 \u0111\u1ee9a con nh\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y. Ch\u1ec9 ch\u01b0a tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n khi gi\u1edd \u0111ang r\u1ed9 tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c con anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n chung nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi anh.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5295","checkdouble":"194112"},{"date":"15:19 09/08","title":"Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/27/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft \u1edf Real, Marcelo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus.</h2><h2>Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Marcelo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Marcelo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Marcelo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/2/Ronaldo-thuc-giuc-Marcelo-den-Juventus--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Marcelo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed l\u00ean t\u1edbi 105 tri\u1ec7u euro. Song c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 CR7 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh &lsquo;c\u01a1 \u0111\u01a1n&rsquo; t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo&nbsp;Tuttosport, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Marcelo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chinh chi\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng m\u00ecnh. Ronaldo v\u00e0 Marcelo l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi nhau \u1edf c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Real su\u1ed1t 9 n\u0103m qua. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1eddi.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Marcelo c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi Ronaldo, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Brazil v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. N\u1ebfu Marcelo ra \u0111i, Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00ecm s\u00e2u v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV&nbsp;Zinedine Zidane v\u00e0 Ronaldo.&nbsp;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00ed do \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia ch\u01b0a t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Marcelo. Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Italia, Juventus ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd b\u00e1n Alex Sandro - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c PSG quan t\u00e2m. Sandro \u0111ang l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 46 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la. Do \u0111\u00f3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juve mua Marcelo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 &nbsp;Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juve. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00ed t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Luka Modric trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pjanic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5294","checkdouble":"194109"}]}